imdb.plot outline: Get excited for "Food Science". Hosted by actress Katy Stoll, this female-driven "science" show features relatable experiments with items that can be found in your kitchen. "Food Science" is fun and fast-paced, proving science isn't just performed in labs by men in white coats. Anyone can be a scientist in their own kitchen.
